reviews.text: Very popular local fastfood cafe of good quality in view of the acceptable price. Can come eat here morning till night! Attractive promotion for members.

Café de Coral is the largest HK style Cafe chain.  Crowded during lunch hours, but the staff try their very best to smooth out the situation.  Lots of enthusiasm at the restaurant.  The pork chop rice with tomato sauce is their most famous dish.  It tastes very good but I personally prefer more cheese.

Hong Kong cafeteria style restaurant.  Order food you want listed as numbers like a1, a2, b3 etc along the wall.  Find a seat, go eat your food with your receipt. Fast, cheap and locally loved.  I ordered the personal hot pot. They always have different food promotions like hot pot for winter.
Good food and service.

reviews.text: 東涌附近只得三間冇理由唔幫襯㗎服務員可以啦有個經理指揮得好勁家
シティゲ－ト近くのフ－ドコ－トで、アウトレットとは別の建物の中にあります。自動券売機でもオ－ダ－できて、オクトパスカ－ドも使えました。ステーキが美味しそうでした。

為何每次在大家樂的東涌富東邨分店，想吃瀨粉時，遲過下午4時，就必定賣完？
分店可否預留至下5：30，距離下午茶完結時段還很遠呢！😩😨
食雪菜肉絲米有玻璃碎，幸好無受傷。
食物質素可接受，但地方大，價錢在東涌己是平價。
